{"tid":2365708,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"司機「和你lunch」襲警非法集結使用蒙面物品罪成 判囚7個月","createTime":"2021-01-14T03:32:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T10:19:13.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"d875f0a3d992303bec6c3532d1c727dfeb04a4db","tid":2365708,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T03:32:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12903\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12903&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuDnF0ojDccr9OXaUhyJR%2F0g%3D&h=dc878624\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12903</a><br />\n<br />\n#東區裁判法院第十庭<br />\n#張志偉裁判官<br />\n#1113中環 #判刑 <br />\n<br />\n👤張(35) <br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n（1）襲擊警務人員<br />\n（2）非法集結<br />\n（3）在非法集結中使用蒙面物品 <br />\n<br />\n詳情：被控於2019年11月13日，中環交易廣場平台，襲擊警沙展A、與其他人士進行非法集結，並使用蒙面物品蒙面。 <br />\n<br />\n控罪(1)認罪<br />\n控罪(2),(3)審訊後定罪<br />\n<br />\n判刑速報~<br />\n判處7個月監禁‼️"},{"pid":"7d07d5340753bac3e57d61981b880fe9e69931cd","tid":2365708,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T03:35:45.000Z","msg":"35歲司機在前年11月的三罷示威中衝撞一名警長，阻止警察將一對被制服的男女帶走，早前承認襲警罪，再被裁定非法集結及在身處非法集結時使用蒙面物品罪成。裁判官張志偉今早在東區裁判法院3罪共判處被告監禁7個月，指雖受襲警員無實際傷勢，但屬最嚴重襲警情節，又指案發時正值中環午飯時間，對公眾威脅極大。<br />\n<br />\n涉案受襲警長A的防暴警隊員陳智勇早前作供稱，案發當日駐守中區警署公眾活動小隊，下午1時許接報到交易廣場平台，看見現場有逾100名黑衣戴口罩的人士聚集破壞，情緒激動，向警方叫囂指罵。<br />\n<br />\n其他警員制服1男1女後，陳及同隊10名隊員圍圈保護2人，退向交易廣場1座玻璃門，期間警告黑衣人不要衝擊不果，黑衣人投擲大量雜物。<br />\n<br />\n穿著灰衣綠長褲、戴黑口罩和眼鏡的被告，於人群前沿2次衝前指罵警員，陳遂持警棍上前驅趕被告。期間被告反抗，並欲搶陳手上圓盾，陳警告後揮棍打被告手部。被告和人群並未散去，被告突然衝向事主警長A面前「想撞埋去」，陳認為被告想襲警，上前支援時遭被告打中左胸，數名警員隨後制服被告。"},{"pid":"bdc05269ba8cbf6917737c38ba0cf0b5f66bd115","tid":2365708,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T03:36:27.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢都襲警"},{"pid":"d88c63c69cb4fc4cd44d84ca6343d6e16efb0d11","tid":2365708,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T03:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f455c2755a5630fc80b6937ee81e8637c60317","tid":2365708,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T03:46:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e397dac11477b3d57f0ef3255e04704de1a7b6e","tid":2365708,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T03:47:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28892ca123013989f25d12de4a7816ddc4affea8","tid":2365708,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T03:52:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc63da4ad470ad774ebc4ddc7506abb38b9c1748","tid":2365708,"uid":26014,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T03:56:55.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">但屬最嚴重襲警情節，又指案發時正值中環午飯時間，對公眾威脅極大。</span> <br />\n啲狗對公眾威脅仲大啦，開槍呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"3da47c82142ddeed6fc5a6a9b974869b8e8a2dba","tid":2365708,"uid":39503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T04:12:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a7e305e65a831c0102656bad78f11f43729c18c","tid":2365708,"uid":55162,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T04:13:50.000Z","msg":"//...警員無實際傷勢，但屬最嚴重襲警情節...//<br />\n<br />\n佢知唔知自己講緊咩"},{"pid":"2e0cb40379c2096ff19243009c64c9ddbf661e73","tid":2365708,"uid":62721,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"1a7e305e65a831c0102656bad78f11f43729c18c","tid":2365708,"uid":55162,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T04:13:50.000Z","msg":"//...警員無實際傷勢，但屬最嚴重襲警情節.../